377
00:24:08,070 --> 00:24:10,200
You're not going to stay here, are you?

378
00:24:21,480 --> 00:24:22,280
I have no idea.

379
00:24:34,980 --> 00:24:35,790
Manager Si.

380
00:24:37,990 --> 00:24:38,820
I...

381
