391
00:24:59,320 --> 00:25:01,260
All of the lanterns come from my family.

392
00:25:01,260 --> 00:25:03,100
The villagers,

393
00:25:03,120 --> 00:25:04,320
especially Jing Chen

394
00:25:04,340 --> 00:25:06,810
